import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { UsersService } from '../users.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-active', templateUrl: './active.component.html', styleUrls: ['./active.component.css'] }) export class ActiveComponent implements OnInit{ users: { name: string, status: string }[] = []; constructor(private usrSer: UsersService) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.users = this.usrSer.users; } }
